title: Bump Documenter to 1.15.0
body: I'd like to see this  backported to various Julia versions so that we benefit from improvements and new features everywhere. But backporting manifest changes can be problematic; it may be easier to just create direct PRs for the 1.10 / 1.12 / 1.13 branches. If desired, I can make PRs for those.
